2. Ran the cantera msi
3. Ran the cantera setup from the cantera folder
4. When I double-clicked on a python script a DOS console window 
flashed on the screen (no error message)
5. If I right click on a script and then choose to edit the script 
and then try to run it from the python console:
ImportError: No module named numarray.libnumeric
6. The offending line in the script is &quot;import from Cantera *&quot;
7. So I found the libnumeric installer for python 2.5 and installed 
it.
8. Same problem.
9. Searched for answers in the forum, haven&#39;t found any (yet)

