it to work? If so, how did you do it? The installation instructions 
just say to run the installer. I found answers for matlab, but I 
don&#39;t have that, nor do I have a complier (at least under winxp) so I 
need to get the winxp installer working with python.

I know next to nothing about python, so how do I tell if libnumeric 
is properly installed? I didn&#39;t see anything obvious on a quick 
glance of the python directory structure. 




